So before jumping into it, I'll just give a quick overview

12
00:00:34,777 --> 00:00:36,038
of what I'll be covering today.

13
00:00:36,919 --> 00:00:38,681
So I'll start off with a brief introduction,

14
00:00:39,221 --> 00:00:42,024
